# Baby, l hear the blues a-calling
Tossed salads and scrambled eggs

303
00:22:10,538 --> 00:22:12,130
# Mercy!

304
00:22:12,374 --> 00:22:18,131
# Maybe l seem a bit confused
Yeah maybe, but l got you pegged!

305
00:22:19,506 --> 00:22:23,215
# But l don't know what to do
With those salads and scrambled eggs

